  "merger_description": "Equans SAS (**Equans**) proposed to acquire 80% of the share capital of CV Services Group Pty Ltd (**CV Services Group**) either directly or through a wholly-owned subsidiary (the\u00a0**Proposed Acquisition**).\n\nEquans is a global energy and technical services company headquartered in France. In Australia, Equans operates through a local subsidiary, which supplies:\n\n* electrical and communications installation;\n* facility management services, including;\n  \n  + installation and maintenance of heating, ventilation and air conditioning (HVAC); and\n  + fire protection products; and\n* audio-visual integration and digital signage.\n\nCV Services Group is an Australian technical services company. It supplies:\n\n* infrastructure services;\n* electrical design, installation and construction;\n* facility management services; and\n* media and signage manufacturing and installation.",
